Author: TreatyPie
Text: w r o n g. Treat yourself, babe! Get a grande (yes, grande, you deserve it) mocha frap with nonfat milk and enjoy those 270 calories! Even if you ate 3 of a meal that was only supposed to be for 1 meal, that’s only a day’s worth! You won’t gain anything from that and a frap! Drink lots of water - you’ll be fine <3
